+    (slot < 0) gets m=0 (the GEMM early-EXITs; its c13/c2 rows stay zero, so
+    the pair contributes nothing) and bumps `miss_ptr` — the runner fetches
+    the missing experts and replays the step. Only the w2-tier tables d[0]
